    <span class="h1 enlighten">How to <b>deal with frozen pipes</b></span>
  </h1>
  <p slot="paragraph">If recent years are anything to go by, we can expect plenty more icy winters. And that could spell trouble for our pipes – and ultimately, our homes.</p>
  <p slot="paragraph">Frozen pipes are a big problem. Not only can they stop your heating and hot water from working properly, they can also burst – causing leaks, or even flooding. So if you think your pipes have frozen over, you’ll need to act quickly to prevent any further damage.</p>
